&lt;p&gt;   Txn commit has a bug for lower versions where it would treat `COORDINATOR_LOAD_IN_PROGRESS` as fatal. This PR fixes the handling of older client to return &lt;br/&gt;
   `COORDINATOR_NOT_AVAILABLE` so that it won&apos;t crash upon doing txn commit. &lt;/p&gt;

